HELP_DESC: List of all Hori's commands with description
LYRICS_NOTHINGFOUND_DESC: I couldn't find song with that title
ARTIST__NOTHINGFOUND_DESC: I couldn't find artist with that name
ERROR_DESC: Please copy text from message below and create bug report on [Github](https://github.com/JustLian/HoriBot) or contact developer on [support server](https://discord.gg/gSvt9TpHkG)
SKIP_NOTPLAYING_DESC: Use /radio on (admins only) to enable radio or /play <query> to play anything from YT/YTMusic
SKIP_JOINVC_DESC: Join same channel as me to use that command!
SKIP_VOTED_DESC: 75% of listeners must vote to skip current song
NO_PREMISSIONS_DESC: You don't have enough permissions to execute that command!
RS_INLIB_DESC: If you know that playlist is not in library report that on our github with your server id (https://github.com/JustLian/HoriBot)
RS_NOT_INLIB_DESC: If you know that playlist is in library report that on our github with your server id (https://github.com/JustLian/HoriBot)
RS_NOT_IN_VC_DESC: You need to join some VC to do that!
SETUP_RADIO_DESC: Use command /radio_settings to setup radio on your server. (You must have Administrator permissions)
RADIO_SETUP: Setting everything up! Currently trying to get your playlist.
RADIO_DISABLED_DESC: Use command /radio on to enable it!
CHECK_RADIO_DESC: To use that feature you need to turn off radio using command /radio off
